Kamu berbohong.

23:05.610 --> 23:06.040
Su.

23:06.300 --> 23:06.960
Tidak.

23:07.590 --> 23:07.880
Su.

23:07.880 --> 23:09.680
Hanya ada Chen Lijian di hatimu.

23:10.590 --> 23:12.270
